About this item

ITEM FEATURES
  • [3 in 1 Charging Station]  The wireless charger conveniently charges for your iPhone, Apple Watch,AirPods,and other devices with wireless charging capability simultaneously. The charging station make powering up your entire desktop and nightstand a breeze,say goodbye tangled cords.Compatible with iPhone 13,12,11 Pro/Max/Mini/Plus,X,XR,XS/Max,SE,8/Plus, iWatch 1-7SE, AirPods 2/pro.
  • [Fast Wireless Charger]  Just place your wireless devices on charging station and a steady, efficient charge begins on contact.After many extreme tests and fan feedback, we use high-power charging chips and world-class electronic to ensure the fast charging quality of charging station.The wireless charger takes about 2-3 hours to give your phone, watch, and earphone a full charge with an equipped 18W adapter.
  • [Safe Wireless Charger Stand]  Wireless charging station for apple with over-current protection, over-voltage protection, over-temperature protection, and foreign object detection function. Reasonable internal circuit of the wireless charging station for apple design prevent overcharge damage to the equipment battery and ensure safe and fast charging of the device.
  • [Foldable Travel Wireless Charger for iphone] The wireless charging station for multiple devices apple offers fast charging for your iphone at home, in the office and on the go due to its compact and folding design. The wireless charger for apple acts as a wireless charger stand holder with angle adjustment.
  • [Case Friendly]  The wireless charger for iphone supports most phone cases not thicker than 0.2 inches/5 mm, so saving the trouble to remove the phone case while charging with wireless charging station (not including cases with magnetic or metal attachments).
  • [What you get]  You will get a 1* 3 in 1 Fast Wireless Charging Station Dock, 1*Type C Cable, QC 3.0 fast power adapter and a user guide. Every charging station we sent to you has gone through a series of quality inspection processes. If you have any questions, please contact us and we'll provide you with a satisfied solution.
